    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it\u2019s like it hasn\u2019t even aged a day! I\u2019ve been super careful with it, so there isn\u2019t a single blemish to be found. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel inside. I'm sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for a great new home for it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
