    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly remarkable specimen that defines showroom quality. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that is absolutely flawless; the paint retains its deep, original luster with zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule, featuring supple, unblemished leather upholstery, pristine carpeting protected by original mats, and a dashboard that looks untouched by time. Every electronic component and convenience feature functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is detailed to a professional standard, and the undercarriage remains remarkably clean. Accompanied by a complete service history and all original keys and manuals, this is an investment-grade vehicle for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
