    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a machine in showroom condition. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically beyond reproach, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery date. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade vehicle.",
