      "description": "Offering a showroom-standard E46 M3, a definitive example of high-revving naturally aspirated engineering. This vehicle features the S54 3.2L inline-six, showcasing impeccable compression across all cylinders and a recently overhauled VANOS system for optimal variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. Crucially, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the bushings have been refreshed with OEM+ components to maintain factory-spec kinematics. With zero paint thickness deviations and a pristine undercarriage, this is a mechanically synchronized masterpiece for the serious collector.",
